statement:
SELECT
	CAST(AVG(originalsurge) AS DOUBLE) AS raw_surge_with_poi
FROM
	ocd_adw.fact_tbl1 AS fact_data_source
LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT
		poi_id AS gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id,
		max(root_poi_id) AS gpi_db_dim_table1__gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__root_poi_id,
		max(parent_poi_id) AS gpi_db_dim_table1__gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__parent_poi_id
	FROM
		gpi_db.dim_table1
	GROUP BY
		1) AS gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1 ON
	CAST(gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1.gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id AS varchar)= CAST(pick_up_poi_id AS varchar)
WHERE
	DATE_TRUNC('hour', stream_time) >= STR_TO_DATE('2025-08-31 17:00:00', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%S')
	AND DATE_TRUNC('hour', stream_time) < STR_TO_DATE('2025-09-07 17:00:00', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%S')
	AND date_id >= 20250829
	AND date_id < 20250909
	AND (country_id = 5
		and city_id in (24)
			and (pick_up_poi_id in ('IT.2CT9360EDADTS')
				or gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1.gpi_db_dim_table1__gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__root_poi_id in ('IT.2CT9360EDADTS')
					or gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1_poi_id__gpi_db_dim_table1.gpi_db_dim_table1__gpi_db_dim_table1_pick_up_poi_id__parent_poi_id in ('IT.2CT9360EDADTS'))
				and vehicle_type_id in (16607, 15990, 15822, 15781, 15780, 15732, 15731, 15692, 15570, 15569, 14890, 14889, 14888, 14887, 14837, 14836, 14409, 14405, 14398, 14397, 13473, 11854, 11853, 11852, 11778, 11777, 11776, 11775, 11675, 11652, 11258, 11257, 10897, 10896, 10895, 10894, 10893, 10892, 10891, 10555, 10554, 5971, 5904, 5742, 5575, 4721, 3500, 2330, 233, 224, 68))
LIMIT 10001;
